'From Squeak3.10beta of 22 July 2007 [latest update: #7137] on 20 November 2007 at 12:58:30 am'!"Change Set:		WideCharacterSet-copy-Patch-M3574-niceDate:			20 November 2007Author:			niceWideCharacterSet copy is shallow: changing a copy changes the original.This is a patch."!!WideCharacterSet methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'nice 11/20/2007 00:57'!postCopy	map := map collect: [:each | each copy]! !!WideCharacterSet reorganize!('comparing' = byteArrayMap hash species wideCharacterMap)('collection ops' add: do: includes: remove: size)('private' bitmap:at: bitmap:do: clearBitmap:at: setBitmap:at:)('testing' hasWideCharacters)('initialize-release' initialize)('converting' complement)('copying' postCopy)!